This paper deals with click models for search engines, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a new model that incorporates externalities and user fatigue, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of key-phrases, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and information science (cs.SI).
